{"tid":1803432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用古惑仔打刧，暴力打擊黃色經濟圈","createTime":"2019-12-30T07:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T07:58:37.000Z","uid":22633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fa51b03ecdc72a5441dd8bcfabbefbadb106029b","tid":1803432,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T07:57:59.000Z","msg":"啲高官，中聯辦廢柴日日喺度屌黃色經濟圈，呢件事幾有成效唔使講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係睇返呢排越黎越多打刧黃店嘅新聞，<br />\n搵古惑仔去打刧黃店，<br />\n好明顯係政府下一步去打擊黃色經濟圈嘅手段，<br />\n道理同黑警專放生藍絲，<br />\n福建幫揸刀扮睇唔到，<br />\n721事件，甚至浮屍自殺冇可疑一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只要你搞嘅係黃店，就話唔夠人手查/查唔到，<br />\n變相直接用暴力打擊黃色經濟圈，同埋你班和理非<br />\n</span><br />\n因為實在太驚黃色經濟圈擴大，<br />\n只要能夠阻止你地而家乜野手段都會用，<br />\n可能下一步就係襲擊黃店入面嘅消費者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家諗諗計，究竟點拆好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">世界越黑暗，我地越要堅持</span>"},{"pid":"2e93585728f9cd5fc09515421e74372f3d1b8cd7","tid":1803432,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T07:58:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家仲有一份未達標 <span style=\"color: red;\">最後兩日</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1802070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1802070</a><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkfY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=6fefd949\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></blockquote>"}]}